{
  "stem": "4189.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put us on a train, on a regular passenger train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they packed us in like sardines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like if there was a compartment that was made for-- was designed to seat eight people, they would stuff in there 15 or 20 people into that compartment.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, no, no food, no water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the trip from Boulogne to Brussels takes approximately six hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we finally we did-- the train actually did go into Belgium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We saw that on the-- looking out the window, we could see that they were going into Belgian territories.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we started to be very happy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We thought they were going to send us back home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when the train arrived in Brussels, they did not let us get off the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they connected another train that came from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was a huge armory that was near Brussels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that armory, which we didn't know at the time, we didn't know this, but they used that armory to round up all the Jews from Belgium, from all the towns from Belgium, from Brussels, from Antwerp, from Liege, Charleroi, all the towns.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they brought them to [NON-ENGLISH] as a, a, a center where they collected all the people-- men, women, and children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they put another train with box cars onto our train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they deported us from there right into Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they gave us numbers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was the 16 transport that left [NON-ENGLISH] at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I had the number of 569 given to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They gave us cards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they gave us, they gave us a card with a string around the neck with a card.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the number was put on 569.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
